longdesc=("The Advanced Linux Sound Architecture (ALSA) provides audio and MIDI functionality to the Linux operating system. OSS (Open Sound System) is an older sound system for Linux that ALSA is replacing. Using the aoss wrapper you can use programs that only support OSS with ALSA without having to load the OSS compatibility kernel modules.")

